description: Finally, a two-bedroom where you don’t have to sacrifice space - welcome to 524 E 6th Street, Unit 3. This thoughtfully designed penthouse condo in the heart of South Boston features 2 bedrooms, a private deck, and an abundance of natural light. Sun-drenched rooms blend timeless charm with modern updates, creating a space that truly has it all. Highlights include gleaming hardwood floors, a cozy fireplace, and a bright, open-concept living and dining area ideal for relaxing or entertaining. Step outside to your private deck - a peaceful city escape - with exclusive roof rights offering even more potential. Additional perks include in-unit laundry, central air, private storage, and skylights. Located in a vibrant neighborhood just moments from Broadway’s shops, restaurants, and public transit.
